VP Academic

I wanted a way to enchance the CS community at Western, and as VP Academic for the Computer Science Undergraduate Society at Western, I get to plan out academic events that help students excel.

Some of the events and workshops my team held included an internship panel with students who had interned at Microsoft, Google, Instagram, and RBC, A TD Bank workshop, a resume editing program, and a Microsoft Azure workshop. We also held a two bar nights because we're not boring people.
